name: SNResultsObserving
desc: The interface your app implements to receive the results of an analysis request.

items.name: func request(SNRequest, didProduce: SNResult)
items.desc: Provides a new analysis result to your app with the specified time range.

items.name: protocol SNResult
items.desc: A protocol that represents sound analysis results.

items.name: func request(SNRequest, didFailWithError: Error)
items.desc: Provides any errors that occur during processing of the request.

items.name: func requestDidComplete(SNRequest)
items.desc: Notifies your app when the analysis request completes normally.
